However, this year the session endsin December at which time H.R. 6631dies, if it has not already been passed byboth hou es of Congress. Passage is all butimpossible at this late date, since Congressrecesses October 2, 1976 for theGeneral Election in November.Another attempt to license the privatehobby breeder may occur in 1977.
